= IMG_LoadTexture_RW =

Load an image directly into a render texture.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
SDL_Texture * IMG_LoadTexture_RW(SDL_Renderer *renderer, SDL_RWops *src, int freesrc);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''renderer'''
|SDL Render
|-
|'''src'''
|RWops
|-
|'''freesrc'''
|can be set so that the RWops is freed after this function is called
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns SDL Texture, or NULL on error

